Lewis Fitz-Gerald https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lewis_Fitz-Gerald 0 Lewis Fitz-Gerald (born 15 November 1958) is an Australian actor, screenwriter and television director. His academic qualifications include PhD (UNE), MA (Comms) UNE, BDA (Acting) NIDA. Fitz-Gerald lectures in Screen and Media Studies at the University of New England (Australia).
